-- Siemens, Workers Extend Pact on Securing German Locations, Jobs
-- B y   M i k e   G a v i n
-- 2010-09-22T10:04:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-22/siemens-workers-extend-pact-on-securing-german-locations-jobs.html
Siemens AG, its central works
council and the IG Metall union have reached an “open-ended
agreement” securing business locations and employment in
Germany, the company said in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
